pageDescription: AI actions are functions that make it easier to work with the AI.

summary.text:
Sends a chat message to the AI.
Returns a promise that contains the response from the AI.
Throws a
[`CasualOSError`](ref:CasualOSError)

if an error occurs while sending the message.

This function can be useful for creating chat bots, or for using an Artificial Intelligence (AI) to process a message.
The message that should be sent to the AI.
The options that should be used.

summary.text:
Generates an image from the given prompt.

Returns a promise that resolves with the Base64 data of the generated image that can be used as the
[`#formAddress`](tags:formAddress)
of a bot.
the request object that describes what the image should look like.
the options for the request.

comment.text:

summary.text:
Generates a [skybox image](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skybox_%28video_games%29) from the given request object.

Returns a promise that resolves with an object that contains a URL to the generated image that can be used as the
[`#formAddress`](tags:formAddress)
of a bot that has
[`#form`](tags:form)
set to
`skybox`
the request object that describes what the skybox should look like.
